pr_review_comment_body:
If you follow my suggestion above, this will become

    if (options.addRelatedPlatforms)

Be careful about spacing. There should be one between 'if' and '(options...'.

To DRY this up a little, I would turn the kinds/labels mapping into data and loop over it. e.g.

```javascript
const kindsLabelMap = {
  [ContentNodeKinds.TOPIC]: 'topics',
...
}

for (const kind of Object.keys(kindsLabelMap)) {
  // if (this.contentsContain(kind)) ...
}
```
